---
title: Easy As Sweet Soy Beef & Pork Noodle Stir-Fry with Baby Broccoli
description: Meet your new weeknight favorite! Juicy beef & pork mince mingles with egg noodles, baby broccoli and a luscious sweet soy glaze that hits all the right notes - savoury, sweet and utterly addictive. Quick to cook and big on flavour, this stir-fry turns your kitchen into a sizzling, saucy adventure. Dinner just got an upgrade!
